
  Dreepy    Dragon Type Pokémon

  After being reborn as a ghost 
  Pokémon, Dreepy wanders the areas 
  it used to inhabit back when 
  it was alive in prehistoric seas. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Dreepy ► Drakloak ► Dragapult

